    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pencils with lead of finely ground, highly compacted charcoal. Less messy, but not as versatile as charcoal sticks.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000018191/Diagram Group and Midgley, Handtools of Arts and Crafts (1981)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Potloden met een stift van fijngemalen, zeer dicht geperst houtskool. Ze zijn minder kliederig maar niet zo veelzijdig bruikbaar als houtskoolstaafjes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052520/Van Beek Art Supplies</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>炭鉛筆是炭磨細成粉後緊密壓製而成；與炭筆相較，炭鉛筆較不易造成髒汙，但是相對較不富變化。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stift mit einer Mine aus fein gemahlener, stark verdichteter Kohle. Weniger schmutzig, aber nicht so vielseitig wie Zeichenkohle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
